Key Match Events: Algeria fell behind early in the 11th minute due to a goal by Thibault Kludge for Togo
Said Benhrahma scored the equalizer for Algeria in the 29th minute
Benhrahma completed his brace by netting a penalty in the 55th minute to put Algeria ahead
Houssem Aouar scored a goal for Algeria in the 68th minute
Amine Gouiri scored a goal for Algeria in the 86th minute
Mohamed Amoura scored a goal for Algeria in the 90+5 minute
Others: The match took place at the 19 May 1956 Stadium in Annaba
The win for Algeria keeps them at the top of Group E in the qualifiers
The teams that played were Algeria and Togo
